<L>__{interior corridor, plush hotel felix}
<A>__{he is standing by an elevator in f.g. keeping watch on a row of room doors including the site of the poker game. felix is an impressive physical specimen whose capacity for brutality is masked by a quiet, deferential manner. when he sees a door open, he moves so as to be out of the shooter's sight as the latter comes toward him. it isn't until the shooter rounds the corner in f.g. and presses the button for the elevator that felix makes his presence known.}
